dialogue.name: Now THIS computes! We're really due for more live performances now!
Well whaddya know? My built-in chromatic synthesizer works like a charm!
See? Just gotta take those baby steps to break out of your shell, Sunny.
I thought we did pretty good! Though I did notice a few viewers click off stream...
This was just part of Sunny's programming. I shouldn't be TOO good of a singer, y'know?
